title: Silobreaker
description:
Silobreaker helps organizations transform data from millions of open and dark web sources into timely, actionable intelligence for a range of use cases.

The OpenCTI Silobreaker connector facilitates the import of Silobreaker Threat data into OpenCTI. The connector connects to the Silobreaker and gather all data from a given date.
short_description: Silobreaker helps organizations transform data from millions of open and dark web sources into timely, actionable intelligence for a range of use cases.
